  <p class="breadcrumbs">You are here: <a href="/en.html?id=4">Government.no</a> / <a href="/en/dep/fin.html?id=216">Ministry of Finance</a> / <a href="/en/dep/fin/The-Ministry.html?id=221">The Ministry</a> / <a href="/en/dep/fin/The-Ministry/Underliggende-etater.html?id=115192">Subordinate Agencies</a> / <span>The Customs and Excise Authorities</span>
